{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2007734913","title":"两条路线斗争的基本问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"76d2d8e182","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"2007734913"}],"tags":[{"id":"877762393f","name":"两条路线斗争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"eb58569ef7","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"2007734913","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的党内指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2ee091bdcf","type":"title","text":"两条路线斗争的基本问题“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"2007734913"},{"id":"eb58569ef7","type":"paragraph","text":"我们党内两条路线斗争，基本问题是在无产阶级夺取政权以后，即新民主主义革命胜利以后，中国究竞走资本主义道路，还是走社会主义道路的问题。资产阶级要走资本主义道路，这是很明显的。在我们共产党内部，我们要走社会主义道路，但有一部分人却认为中国是个很穷困的国家，中国资本主义发展水平很低，不能发展社会主义，必须在一段时间内走资本主义道路，然后再走社会主义道路。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"2007734913"},{"id":"8aac2024e4","type":"paragraph","text":"走什么道路问题，解放初期有这个问题，现在仍然有这个问题。苏联搞了五十多年，仍是这个问题","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"2007734913"}],"page":{"id":"8578dc05ba","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"2007734913","start":386,"end":386}}}},"__N_SSG":true}